::Skulletron::

	Skulletron looked at Feline as she looked at him with her hand on his
shoulder.  It sounded like he would be working with her.  No matter what
the case, he wasn't going to let her take command over him, unless Zardus
made strict orders for her to.  Skulletron studied Feline as she talked to
Zardus.  He'd better be careful, he might just get blown away by her
amazing beauty.
